-- Bank Group Says Greece Will Survive Crisis, Tagesspiegel Reports
-- B y   J u l i e   C r u z
-- 2012-02-19T13:40:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-19/bank-group-says-greece-will-survive-crisis-tagesspiegel-reports.html
Greece  will survive its government
debt crisis, Tagesspiegel reported, citing Hans Reckers,
managing director of  Germany ’s VOeB association of public banks.  The country will regain its “competitiveness” and
“creditworthiness,” Tagesspiegel cited Reckers as saying.
Financial restructuring is “the only option,” Reckers told
Tagesspiegel.  To contact the reporter on this story:
